</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>RegOffset</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>is the register offset of the register (defined at the top of this file).</para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>The 32-bit value of the register.</para></simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>C-style signature: u32 <ref refid="group__dptxss_1ga53f6015a16b096337cc3e1f18c2acf71" kindref="member">XDpTxSs_ReadReg(UINTPTR BaseAddress, u32 RegOffset)</ref> </para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
